1- Anytime you need to work with new services don't forget to add it to the "requirements.txt" file and then run the below command:
"pip3 install -r requirements.txt" or you can use the CLI directly to install the service as:
"pip3 install aws-cdk.aws-iam".

2- Remember to activate the virtual environment with the fallowing command "source .env/bin/activate"

3- To remove metadata from the templates go to the root of this directory in the cdk.json file add variable:

"versionReporting" : false